nderful idea, then you are a fool, and should be ashamed about asking other people for help even when you need it because you haven't given back to other people.<br><br>The short of it: This whole discussion is ridiculous, if only people would think about the consequences, even in just a game...<br>&nbsp;<br>~Nobbynob Littlun<br>Crystal Oracle, Druzzil Ro server</td></tr>
